### 🔐 Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5070/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john.doe",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### 🔑 Login and get JWT
POST http://localhost:5070/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john.doe",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### 🧪 GET all user-group assignments (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5070/api/usergroups
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### 🛠 Assign user to group
POST http://localhost:5070/api/usergroups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "userId": "PUT-USER-ID-HERE",
  "groupId": "PUT-GROUP-ID-HERE"
}

###

### ✅ Approve user in group
PUT http://localhost:5070/api/usergroups/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "userId": "PUT-USER-ID-HERE",
  "groupId": "PUT-GROUP-ID-HERE"
}

###

### 📜 Get all permissions
GET http://localhost:5070/api/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### 📋 Get all roles
GET http://localhost:5070/api/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### ➕ Create a new role
POST http://localhost:5070/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "NewManager",
  "permissionIds": [
    "PUT-PERMISSION-ID-1-HERE",
    "PUT-PERMISSION-ID-2-HERE"
  ]
}

###

### 🔁 Assign permission to role
POST http://localhost:5070/api/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### ❌ Remove permission from role
DELETE http://localhost:5070/api/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###

### 🧼 Delete a role
DELETE http://localhost:5070/api/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}